* formula_28 and formula_29 are partial derivatives (rate of change in time, with location fixed) of the magnetic and electric field;
* formula_30 is the permeability of a vacuum (4 × 10−7 H/m), and formula_31 is the permittivity of a vacuum (8.85 × 10−12 F/m);

